Package: soccerAnimate
Type: Package
Title: Creates 2D animations of soccer tracking data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person(given = "Ismael",
                family = "Gómez",
         role = c("aut", "cre"),
         email = "ismaelgomezs@gmail.com")
Maintainer: Ismael Gómez Schmidt <ismaelgomezs@gmail.com>
Description: This packages allows you to create 2D animations of soccer tracking data.
    In addition to that it also provides functions for complementary task like: 
    a) to get tidy data from Metrica Sport data provider, 
    b) to find out which frames you would like to animate searching by event types.
